207
00:10:16,192 --> 00:10:17,133
that really helps.

208
00:10:17,433 --> 00:10:20,373
That's generally going to be somebody

209
00:10:20,393 --> 00:10:21,273
who's made a deal before.

210
00:10:22,405 --> 00:10:25,285
If you know someone like this, you probably do.

211
00:10:25,305 --> 00:10:26,145
And if you don't, you don't.

212
00:10:26,226 --> 00:10:27,686
So harping on this isn't useful.

213
00:10:28,306 --> 00:10:30,546
You can also approach at a convention with a demo.

214
00:10:30,666 --> 00:10:31,527
This is a little harder.

215
