Your pitch better be fucking locked in perfect

216
00:10:35,667 --> 00:10:37,728
because you're gonna get disregarded really quickly

217
00:10:37,768 --> 00:10:38,768
if you're not careful.

218
00:10:40,268 --> 00:10:43,149
Usually you're not looking for like a big two-hour demo

219
00:10:43,189 --> 00:10:43,649
at this point.

220
